{
  "stem": "19441.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 405.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It didn't interest them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They, they, certain, certain SS men didn't.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because those was the selection during the day-- and so she said, so I made notes on this in case he saw.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't come to check for paper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He saw me writing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But-- so I sent the people back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she was-- she knew me from the first minute.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the news travel fast, so she heard how I care for people and how I explain to people, and how I tried to help people.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So when she was in charge, so she put me in charge of a barrack.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so I had-- I was here two, three weeks, then she pulls me out, and she puts me somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she kept changing the barracks you were in charge of.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I tell you why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because according what nationality came in-- and there came in non-Jewish nationality.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, it came in Czech non-Jewish people there, and there was the whole family of the president, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So Magda, you are going to take the Czechs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she put me there in charge.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, I looked after them, that, that it should be running properly, the barrack, that they should have the food, the drink, the bread, the butter.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The barrack should be clean.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so much so that a lot of people had diarrhea, and those who was living on the third bunk, till they came down, it was impossible.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- as it doesn't sound nice to talk about it, but they finished themselves up in the dish, which was their food dish, and then they threw the, the excrement--",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "-- yeah-- through the, the window, because the window wasn't-- it wasn't glass in it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just a frame.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Glass wasn't in it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
